title: Looking For Friends
body:
I play on the OCE server and am looking for some cool people to play with. 
I'm currently level 12 and plan on grinding up to 30 before starting ranked.
Both girls and boys and both acceptable,, 
/add me if you're interested

   -hyper cat

^-^"'

replies.body: Hi there, what is your account name?
Feel free to connect to https://discord.gg/Y93kJJN. A competitive OCE gaming discord which is full of active league players! All happy to play and teach every aspect of the game!
